description: InactivityProfile:  Records of inactivity profiles for different cells in a RAN, specifying their identifiers, location, data type, and version.  `dateTime`: Timestamp of the record; `Area_Name`: RAN area name; `CellId`: Unique identifier of the cell; `Id2`: Redundant cell identifier; `Id3`:  Ancillary identifier (likely constant); `Id4`: Inactivity profile identifier (likely constant); `vsDataType`: Data type identifier; `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format; `InactivityProfile.inactivityProfileId`:  Inactivity profile identifier.
